# gstack is a bundled skill collection cloned by install-skills.sh.
# 250MB+ with its own .git — not commitable. install-skills.sh clones it
# fresh and runs its ./setup to symlink the bundle into each agent.
# Sub-skill wrappers (gstack-*.md) are generated by build.py only when
# gstack/ is installed; they come and go with the install state.
gstack/
gstack-*.md
